 The virus went in for the kill. It consumed the entire spark. It was now 
extinquished. There was no machine that could keep it from stopping for it 
was to late. The virus finished the job and the spark burst. Sending forth an 
explosion. This was a natural reaction to the  destruction of a spark by the 
virus. The explosion should have enough power to completley destroy hell 
beat's body though it didnt matter for the spark was dead but do some damage 
to the object 30 feet near it. Hell Beast is dead.
